[1842-1853], who published only a figure without application of binomial nomenclature. It was subsequenly described by Jacquinot, J. & Guichenot, M.A. 1853. Reptiles et Poissons. Paris : Roret Vol. 7(1) xvi 780 pp. p. 200, also described this taxon as a new 'unpublished species'. The series on which Duméril, Bibron & Duméril based their description included material 'probably from Australia'; this description is included in the above synonymy pending resolution of the authorship and type fixation of Dendrophis lineolata
